I am so proud to collaborate with Forever52 India for Khubsurat Bharat Ki Khubsurat Beti! 🌟
The grand finale contest starts today, and it’s a dream opportunity for aspiring makeup artists and content creators.
 ✨ 3 grand winners will each receive ₹5 lakhs in cash and a 3-day trip to Dubai, where they will enhance their skills, learn from experts, and excel in professional makeup artistry, to kickstart their journey to becoming top makeup artists and creators.

This is your chance to shine, grow, and make your dreams come true! 💖 Best of luck to all participants! 🌟

How to Register for KBKB:
1. Visit the Forever52 website or click the link in bio on Instagram.
2. Register using your mobile number and email address to receive your unique registration number.
3. Create a stunning bridal look using Forever52 products.
4. Share your makeup journey, passion, and dreams in a reel.
5. Post the reel on your Instagram, tag @forever52india and mention your registration number.
For more details, visit the KBKB registration page or connect with the Forever52 India team on Instagram.
Best of luck! May the most talented artists achieve their dreams. 🌟
